------------------------------------------------------------------------

Information about compiling and installing MP3Blaster on your system is listed
in the file called 'INSTALL'.

This version of MP3Blaster is tested on:
Linux/i386 (libc6)
Linux/i386 (libc5)
Linux/alpha 
OpenBSD/alpha
FreeBSD/i386

There's no manual yet, but you can press 'h' in mp3blaster at startup
to get an overview of all the keypresses.
